{"tid":1787050,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中超青島黃海球員耶耶托尼：「奧斯爾不應批評中國人權！」","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:55:36.000Z","uid":9030,"like":11,"dislike":285,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2484d2beebdbb71daa4c212b2d64c51ca875b4","tid":1787050,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"曾效力巴塞羅那及曼城的科特迪瓦中場耶耶托尼，評論阿仙奴中場奧斯爾批評中國打壓新疆維吾爾族人的貼文，認為對方不應該發表有關言論。耶耶托尼說，作為足球員應該留在足球世界，因為伊斯蘭教是一個複雜的議題，牽涉其中會引來很多問題。現時效力青島黃海的耶耶托尼說，自己很喜歡足球，一直堅守不牽涉政治的宗旨。"},{"pid":"908bdf4071795142e01c613b1904e424e7c7f360","tid":1787050,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1239570&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BugmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=76bc5c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1239570</a>"},{"pid":"979983a716caaa690322dcccab1e1c54f5e5ced2","tid":1787050,"uid":48315,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"自己要由世界頂級既球會轉去呢啲第三世界球會<br />\n好心就出小句聲 唔覺得7既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5f952ecd894ad7198d9e306d92318ab16744dd","tid":1787050,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a78b1291b3cfe160c9c00a65da978cba3b68956","tid":1787050,"uid":7043,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"生活每一部分都係政治<br />\n邊有得避而不談"},{"pid":"8f51b6f18399369345b2b0a51c24e0c947c87f38","tid":1787050,"uid":10199,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"足球界LBJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji